---
export interface Props {
  lang?: 'en' | 'de';
}
const { lang = 'en' } = Astro.props;
---

<section class="problem" id="the-problem">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="problem__eyebrow section-fade">
      {lang === 'de' ? 'Das Problem' : 'The Problem'}
    </p>

    <h2 class="problem__heading section-fade">
      <span class="problem__heading-line1">{lang === 'de' ? 'Was in Ihrer Organisation' : 'What goes unheard'}</span>
      <span class="problem__heading-line2">{lang === 'de' ? 'ungehört bleibt.' : 'costs organisations everything.'}</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="problem__cols">
      <div class="problem__col section-fade" style="--delay: 0ms">
        <div class="problem__col-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
            <path d="M10 2a8 8 0 100 16A8 8 0 0010 2zm0 4v4m0 4h.01" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="problem__col-title">
          {lang === 'de' ? 'Die Wissenslücke' : 'The knowledge gap'}
        </h3>
        <p class="problem__col-body">
          {lang === 'de'
            ? "Es lebt in den Köpfen der Menschen. 80 % des operativen Wissens wird nie aufgeschrieben. 42 % dessen, was jeder Mitarbeiter weiß, kann kein Kollege abdecken."
            : "It lives in people's heads. 80% of operational knowledge is never written down. 42% of what each employee knows, no colleague can cover."}
        </p>
        <p class="problem__col-body problem__col-body--callout">
          {lang === 'de'
            ? "Bei einer Fusion, Restrukturierung oder strategischen Neuausrichtung entscheidet genau dieses Wissen über den Erfolg."
            : "During a merger, a restructuring, a strategic pivot — that's exactly the knowledge that decides whether it works."}
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="problem__col section-fade" style="--delay: 100ms">
        <div class="problem__col-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
            <path d="M3 10h14M3 5h14M3 15h8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="problem__col-title">
          {lang === 'de' ? 'Warum bestehende Tools scheitern' : 'Why existing tools fail'}
        </h3>
        <p class="problem__col-body">
          {lang === 'de'
            ? "Ihre Tools hören nur das, was sie fragen. Umfragen stellen 12 Fragen und erhalten 12 Antworten. Berater interviewen 20 Personen in 90 Tagen. Townhalls verdichten Erkenntnisse zu Konsens."
            : "Your tools only hear what they ask. Surveys ask 12 pre-set questions and get 12 pre-set answers. Consultants interview 20 people over 90 days. Town halls compress insight into consensus."}
        </p>
        <p class="problem__col-body problem__col-body--callout">
          {lang === 'de'
            ? "Niemand bringt ans Licht, was man nicht zu fragen wusste — und in dieser Lücke scheitern Transformationen lautlos."
            : "None of them surface what they didn't know to ask — and that gap is where transformations quietly fail."}
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="problem__cta-wrap section-fade">
      <a href="#request-pilot" class="problem__cta">
        {lang === 'de' ? 'Jetzt lösen' : 'Solve it now'}
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M2.5 7h9M7.5 3l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Styles bleiben unverändert wie in deinem Original */
  .problem {
    padding: var(--space-8) 0; /* Nutzt jetzt das Augusta-Spacing */
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-surface-dark);
    background-color: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  }

  /* ... (Rest deines Styles) ... */
</style>